explanation: [0-0] A woman in camouflage clothing is kneeling in front of a wire mesh fence, her back to the camera. A pile of snow chunks is visible on the ground beyond the fence, along with some patchy, messy vegetation. The woman is holding a red container with a white bottom in her left hand.

[0-10] A gray rabbit runs out from the right and jumps onto the woman's right leg. The woman quickly raises her right hand holding the food upward, and the rabbit follows her hand, climbing up repeatedly to reach for the food. During the climb, the rabbit's feet occasionally hit the bottom of the container in the woman's hand. Outside the fence behind the woman, an animal can be seen watching them. The woman, with her right hand raised, turns to the right under the rabbit's onslaught and then leans forward. Finally, the rabbit jumps down and runs out of the frame from the left. The woman turns her head back, smiles, and extends her right hand backward.
